document_data.name: Swonaku Kung's Tavern
document_data.mainbody: '''Swonaku Kung's Tavern''' was a tavern in the city of [[Tu Pe]] in [[Koryo]] around [[1357 DR]]. It lay in the floating city, close to the second of the stone bastions that guarded the [[Tenasu Ferry]] route.
